➜7万差价多22项配置！商务接待，别克GL8和传祺GM8该怎么选？
http://www.sohu.com/a/415954693_99994080	36986
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200901/55d4b1ae278d42adbdc16a175d96231d.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200901/50bf6d105c65415187bc84967a1c0aa1.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>本文编辑：</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200901/4beebef1b2a44630a12ec59028964567.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>写在前面：</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
